msgstr "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frontend for the symmetric encryption functionality of GPG."
msgstr "Začelje za funkcionalnost simetričnega šifriranja GPG."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>symmy</command> <arg rep=\"repeat\"><replaceable>OPTIONS</"
"replaceable></arg> <arg rep=\"repeat\"><replaceable>FILES</replaceable></arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>symmy</command> <arg rep=\"repeat\"><replaceable>OPTIONS</"
"replaceable></arg> <arg rep=\"repeat\"><replaceable>FILES</replaceable></arg>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "OPIS"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>symmy</command> is a simple application that can be used to encrypt "
"or decrypt one or more files using the symmetric encryption functionality of "
"GPG. A file encrypted by <command>symmy</command> can be decrypted by anyone "
"who has access to the GPG program and the encryption key."
msgstr ""
"<command>symmy</command> je preprosta aplikacija, ki jo je mogoče uporabiti "
"za šifriranje ali dešifriranje ene ali več datotek s funkcijo simetričnega "
"šifriranja GPG. Datoteko, šifrirano z <command>symmy</command>, lahko "
"dešifrira vsak, ki ima dostop do programa GPG in šifrirnega ključa."

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>symmy</command> can also be used from &dolphin; or &plasma; Folder "
"View thanks to the <guimenuitem>Encrypt</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Decrypt</guimenuitem> items in the context menu."
msgstr ""
"<command>symmy</command> lahko uporabite tudi iz &dolphin; ali &plasma; "
"Pogled mape zahvaljujoč elementoma <guimenuitem>Šifriraj</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Dešifriraj</guimenuitem> v priročnem meniju."

#. Tag: title
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "ENCRYPTION"
msgstr "ŠIFRIRANJE"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can encrypt one or more files by writing their paths after the "
"<option>encrypt</option> option. You can also select them in &dolphin; or "
"&plasma; Folder View and click the <guimenuitem>Encrypt</guimenuitem> entry "
"in the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Eno ali več datotek lahko šifrirate tako, da njihove poti napišete za "
"možnostjo <option>encrypt</option>. Izberete jih lahko tudi v &dolphin; ali "
"&plasma; Pogled mape in v kontekstnem meniju kliknite vnos "
"<guimenuitem>Šifriraj</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you cannot encrypt a folder. If you need to do that, you should "
"compress the folder and then encrypt the resulting archive. It's also not "
"possible to encrypt remote files or files that are already encrypted."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da mape ne morete šifrirati. Če morate to storiti, morate mapo "
"stisniti in nato šifrirati nastali arhiv. Prav tako ni mogoče šifrirati "
"oddaljenih datotek ali datotek, ki so že šifrirane."

#. Tag: title
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing an Encryption Key"
msgstr "Izbira ključa za šifriranje"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>symmy</command> will ask you a password (or passphrase) that will "
"be used as encryption key for <emphasis>all</emphasis> the selected files. "
"You should choose a strong encryption key and you should store it in a "
"secure place (such as a password manager). If you need to send the key to "
"another person, you should do so over a secure channel (for example, by "
"meeting in person)."
msgstr ""
"<command>symmy</command> vas bo vprašal za geslo (ali frazo), ki bo "
"uporabljeno kot ključ za šifriranje za <emphasis>vse</emphasis> izbrane "
"datoteke. Izberite močan šifrirni ključ in ga shranite na varno mesto (kot "
"je upravitelj gesel). Če morate ključ poslati drugi osebi, to storite po "
"varnem kanalu (na primer na osebnem srečanju)."

#. Tag: title
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "GPG Requirement"
msgstr "Zahteva GPG"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>symmy</command> uses GPG to perform the actual encryption, so it "
"assumes that the <command>gpg-agent</command> process is running and "
"properly configured."
msgstr ""
"<command>symmy</command> uporablja GPG za izvedbo dejanskega šifriranja, "
"zato predpostavlja, da se postopek <command>gpg-agent</command> izvaja in je "
"pravilno konfiguriran."

#. Tag: title
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing an Encryption Operation"
msgstr "Upravljanje operacije šifriranja"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The encryption operation will take some time depending on the number of "
"files and on their size. You can track the progress of the operation from "
"the notification applet provided by &plasma;. From the notification plasmoid "
"you can also abort the encryption operation if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Postopek šifriranja bo trajal nekaj časa, odvisno od števila datotek in "
"njihove velikosti. Napredek operacije lahko spremljate iz programčka za "
"obvestila, ki ga nudi &plasma;. Iz obvestilnega plazmoida lahko po potrebi "
"tudi prekinete operacijo šifriranja."

#. Tag: title
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "DECRYPTION"
msgstr "DEŠIFRIRANJE"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can decrypt one or more encrypted files by writing their paths after the "
"<option>decrypt</option> option. You can also select them in &dolphin; or "
"&plasma; Folder View and click the <guimenuitem>Decrypt</guimenuitem> entry "
"in the context menu. Note that this entry will be visible only when "
"selecting encrypted files."
msgstr ""
"Eno ali več šifriranih datotek lahko dešifrirate tako, da njihove poti "
"napišete za možnostjo <option>decrypt</option>. Izberete jih lahko tudi v "
"&dolphin; ali &plasma; Pogled mape in v kontekstnem meniju kliknite vnos "
"<guimenuitem>Dešifriraj</guimenuitem>. Upoštevajte, da bo ta vnos viden le "
"pri izbiri šifriranih datotek."

#. Tag: title
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing a Decryption Operation"
msgstr "Upravljanje operacije dešifriranja"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The decryption operation will take some time depending on the number of "
"files and on their size. You can track the progress of the operation from "
"the notification applet provided by &plasma;. From the notification plasmoid "
"you can also abort the decryption operation if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Postopek dešifriranja bo trajal nekaj časa, odvisno od števila datotek in "
"njihove velikosti. Napredek operacije lahko spremljate iz programčka za "
"obvestila, ki ga nudi &plasma;. Iz obvestilnega plazmoida lahko po potrebi "
"tudi prekinete operacijo dešifriranja."

#. Tag: title
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "OPTIONS"
msgstr "MOŽNOSTI"

#. Tag: option
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "-e, --encrypt"
msgstr "-e, --encrypt"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Encrypts the given list of files after asking a passphrase. This option is "
"implicitly set if there are no other options."
msgstr ""
"Šifrira podani seznam datotek po tem, ko zahteva geslo. Ta možnost je "
"implicitno nastavljena, če ni drugih možnosti."

#. Tag: option
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "-d, --decrypt"
msgstr "-d, --decrypt"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Decrypts the given list of files after asking the decryption key. Note that "
"<option>encrypt</option> and <option>decrypt</option> are mutually exclusive."
msgstr ""
"Dešifrira dani seznam datotek po tem, ko zahteva ključ za dešifriranje. "
"Upoštevajte, da se <option>encrypt</option> in <option>decrypt</option> "
"medsebojno izključujeta."

#. Tag: option
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "-h, --help"
msgstr "-h, --help"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows a brief synopsis and description of the command line options."
msgstr "Prikazuje kratek povzetek in opis možnosti ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: option
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --version"
msgstr "-v, --version"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows the version of this program."
msgstr "Prikazuje različico tega programa."

#. Tag: option
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "--author"
msgstr "--author"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows information about the author of this program."
msgstr "Prikazuje podatke o avtorju tega programa."

#. Tag: option
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "--license"
msgstr "--license"

#. Tag: para
#: man-symmy.1.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows information about the license of this program."
msgstr "Prikazuje informacije o licenci tega programa."
